Support these block patterns:

 - <code>&#x5b;&#x5b;url&#x5d;&#x5d;</code> → `http://127.0.0.1:8080`
 - <code>&#x5b;&#x5b;url.protocol&#x5d;&#x5d;</code> → `http://`
 - <code>&#x5b;&#x5b;url.host&#x5d;&#x5d;</code> → `127.0.0.1:8080`
 - <code>&#x5b;&#x5b;url.port&#x5d;&#x5d;</code> → `:8080`
 - <code>&#x5b;&#x5b;url.path&#x5d;&#x5d;</code> → `/foo/bar`
 - <code>&#x5b;&#x5b;url.query&#x5d;&#x5d;</code> → `?foo=bar&baz=qux`
 - <code>&#x5b;&#x5b;url.current&#x5d;&#x5d;</code> → `http://127.0.0.1:8080/foo/bar/1?foo=bar&baz=qux`